description:
An application submitted under Section 96a of the Town & Country Planning Act 1990 for a non material amendment in connection with the planning permission reference 16/3024/R, dated 20/03/2017, for the submission of Reserved Matters (Appearance, Landscaping, Layout and Scale), pursuant to condition 2 of Outline Planning Permission reference 13/0117/O, dated 19/06/2013, for 764 residential units and 602 (GEA) sqm of non-residential floorspace within the A Blocks (Phases 9/10/11/12/13/14) and revised landscaping details for the northern part of the Waterfront Park to allow:
• Alterations to the Lantern Windows (Blocks A1 – A4);  
• Replacement Floorplates to reflect changes to windows and unit mix (Blocks A1 – A4); 
• Redistribution of Unit Mix across Blocks A1 and A2; and 
• Amendments to the approved residential entrances (Blocks A1 – A4).
